creator: footbao.world
descriptionHtml:
If it’s football, it’s on footbao.

Everything about the day to day of football you can now find on the largest social network in the football world. An exclusive platform for fans, amateur or professional players, scouts, clubs or those interested in the sport that moves the most crowds on the planet.

On footbao you can like, comment, share content, gain relevance and be discovered either by other users or even by brands and national and international teams.

Do you want to be a great ace or have fun with football?
Go head first into this world.

Do you want to post as a player? Then create videos with your best plays and showing off your skills. And after, with this content of your own, you can receive scores and start entering an international ranking of great football talents.

Do you want to post cool content as a football fan? Unleash your creativity and let
users rate through likes and, if it becomes a hit, you can be part of the footbao ranking of the best fan videos.

On footbao, you can set your preferences and receive the most relevant content. But don’t worry, different content from the world of football will still be shown to you and you can change these preferences whenever you want.
